short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add in-season player values and projections to your Yahoo, ESPN, CBS, or Fantrax fantasy league website

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Projectile extension adds in-season player values onto your league website, using FanGraphs' player projections.

Values are fully customized for your league settings! It's a great way to evaluate add/drop and trade decisions, especially if your league format differs from a site's default rankings.

It currently works with leagues hosted on almost any platform: Yahoo, ESPN, CBS, Fantrax, or NFBC.

Newly-relevant players will be added periodically. If there's a player you want added, send me their player IDs from FanGraphs and the league site, and I'll make sure they are added.
